<HEADLINE> Arizona RB Mario Bates Arrested  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   SCOTTSDALE, Ariz. (AP) -- Arizona Cardinals running back Mario
Bates was arrested Tuesday on domestic violence charges after
allegedly slapping his girlfriend.
