<HEADLINE> Dow Rises 320; Nasdaq Falls 123  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- The Dow Jones industrial average soared more
than 300 points today as investors moved money that has streamed
out of the technology sector this week into long-forgotten
industrial stocks.
</P>
