</P>
<P>
   According to preliminary calculations, the Standard &AMP; Poor's 500
rose 33.01 to 1,392.16.
</P>
<P>
   Advancing issues outnumbered decliners by a 12-to-7 margin on
the New York Stock Exchange, with 1,920 up, 1,123 down and 441
unchanged.
</P>
<P>
   NYSE volume totaled 1.30 million shares as of 4 p.m., vs. 1.08
billion in the previous session.
</P>
<P>
   The Russell 2000 index of smaller companies fell 14.43 to
558.56.
</P>
</TEXT>
